title: Amplify Digital Delivery
description: Amplify Digital Delivery boosts the knowledge and skills of our Digital Delivery professionals in Accenture Interactive. This training brings together all levels of Acquity Digital Platform teams to connect with each other face-to-face, share ideas, learn from each other, and appreciate the awesome work that we collectively accomplish. Through Amplify Digital Delivery , participants will build a higher level of Digital Delivery Skills by • Refreshing Core Delivery proficiencies - to maintain delivery rigor and discipline • Developing Advanced Digital Delivery expertise - to adapt to new Digital ecosystem needs • Appreciating unique Digital project innovations - to nurture creative problem solving • Understanding the full breadth of Accenture Interactive capabilities and differentiators – to identify new opportunities for new and existing clients • Deepening their relationships by building stronger internal networks – to learn and support each other as one cohesive team
